# SPDX-License-Identifier: Apache-2.0
# Fableton instance crontab — install with: crontab deploy/crontab.example
# (merges: keep the auto-deploy line if already installed)
#
# Prerequisites for the studio lines (studio/README.md § Runtime):
#   - Claude Code on the host, authenticated: `claude setup-token`
#   - gh authenticated with a repo-scoped token. Least privilege (issue
#     #101): a FINE-GRAINED token with Contents, Pull requests, and Issues
#     read/write on the world repo ONLY — no workflow permission, and
#     ideally issued by a NON-ADMIN machine account with Write role, so
#     branch protection binds the pantheon (an owner/admin token can pass
#     `gh pr merge --admin` and step around the review boundary). The
#     agents read text written by anonymous visitors; assume injection and
#     contain, don't trust.
#   - studio working clone at /opt/fableton-studio (never the deploy clone)

# Engine auto-deploy: track origin/main, rebuild when it moves
*/2 * * * * flock -n /run/fableton-deploy.lock /opt/fableton/deploy/auto-deploy.sh >> /var/log/fableton-deploy.log 2>&1

# The pantheon (UTC): steward every 4h · sprite at 08:30/18:30 · council at 09:00
0 */4 * * * flock -n /run/fableton-steward.lock /opt/fableton-studio/studio/bin/run.sh steward >> /var/log/fableton-studio.log 2>&1
30 8,18 * * * flock -n /run/fableton-qa.lock /opt/fableton-studio/studio/bin/run.sh qa >> /var/log/fableton-studio.log 2>&1
0 9 * * * flock -n /run/fableton-council.lock /opt/fableton-studio/studio/bin/run.sh council >> /var/log/fableton-studio.log 2>&1
